<br>
Entry fee will be 1800 pp per person. Contest to be held July 13 at 5 EST.<br>
<br>
1.    Any and all dropped loot that is useable by Shadowknights is allowed in the competiton, examples of this would be Sword of Pain, Blood Ember Armor, Goblin earring, etc etc. Yes, this means you can use clickable items.<br>
<br>
2.   NO TRADESKILL ITEMS ALLOWED- pretty much self explanitory, but for those a little dense, that means no items that are player made. Examples Shaman Potions, SoW, Shrink, Resist increase, etc.<br>
ONLY EXCEPTION TO THIS IS JEWELRY  AND ARMOR THAT IS CRAFTED, you are allowed to wear Player Crafted Jewelry and Armor. <br>
<br>
