<br>
4. All contestants will start out completely debuffed and will have a small time frame to buff themselfs prior to conmencement of the fight. Arrangements have been made to help prevent outside assistance from fellow players.<br>
<br>
5. ALL SPELLS IN SHADOWKNIGHT ARSENAL are allowed, if its in your spellbook, then you can cast it, from Fears all the way to pets and anything else you may wish to throw out there.<br>
<br>
6. All contestants will be expected to duel, though jousting and range manuevering are allowed, running to hell and back to keep out of melee will not be allowed. Running in a continous large circle just to build mana and/or HP and to evade your opponent will not be allowed either.<br>
<br>
